The ALTdot COMedy Lounge is Toronto's most popular alternative comedy show. It runs every Monday at The Rivoli (where The Kids in the Hall frequently performed, and began in the 1990s. In 2005 a Tuesday show, The Sketch Comedy Lounge, was added. The show is produced by Morgan Flood and Lorne Perlmutar.
